WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.672 --> 00:00:05.172
Zhang Peizan: Yes, I came back from walking the horses that day

2
00:00:05.172 --> 00:00:09.122
Zhang Peizan: Just when I walked to the garden, I heard the young lady and her fiancé talking.

3
00:00:09.122 --> 00:00:11.232
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

4
00:00:11.232 --> 00:00:16.892
Zhang Peizan: She asked him to come to the garden in the middle of the night to get gold. Feelings of greed stirred in my heart at that moment.

5
00:00:16.892 --> 00:00:19.462
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

6
00:00:19.462 --> 00:00:23.902
♪ Chorus (singing): He said that he stole a hairpin because he was greedy for gold, ♪

7
00:00:23.902 --> 00:00:29.352
♪ Chorus (singing): and quietly waited outside the garden for Xuechun. ♪

8
00:00:29.352 --> 00:00:39.902
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

9
00:00:39.902 --> 00:00:51.000
♪ Chorus (singing): He clapped his hands three times so that the gate would open, and he could exchange the hairpin for money without any hindrance. ♪

10
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.982
Xuechun: Mr. Lin,

11
00:00:52.982 --> 00:00:55.982
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

12
00:00:55.982 --> 00:01:00.082
Xuechun: you must not let my lady’s kindness go to waste.

13
00:01:00.082 --> 00:01:03.002
Xuechun: It's getting late, please go back.

14
00:01:03.002 --> 00:01:07.000
[Peking opera orchestra plays]

15
00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:29.000
♪ Chorus (singing): Flustered, legs trembling, he fell to the ground and ruined his plan. ♪

16
00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:31.982
Xuechun: Mr. Lin?

17
00:01:31.982 --> 00:01:33.192
Chorus: Xuechun recognized who it was and shouted loudly.

18
00:01:33.192 --> 00:01:33.982
Xuechun: Ah, it’s you!

19
00:01:33.982 --> 00:01:36.002
Zhang Peizan: Don't shout. If you shout, I will kill you.

20
00:01:36.002 --> 00:01:40.002
♪ Chorus (singing): One mistake of his caused her soul to travel to the underworld. ♪

21
00:01:40.002 --> 00:01:41.872
Xuechun: Help!

22
00:01:41.872 --> 00:01:44.202
Zhang Peizan: I saw Lin coming over just when I managed to hide the knife and the gold.

23
00:01:44.202 --> 00:01:46.402
Zhang Peizan: So, he became my scapegoat!